Interface ChoiceListListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EditFragmentActivity, EditFragmentContentActivity, EditFragmentInfoActivity

    public interface ChoiceListListener
    The ChoiceListListener interface is an interface that must be implemented by any activity using a ChoiceListFragment. This interface is to ensure that the activity implements the onChoiceSelected callback function to correctly handle item selection in the ListFragment.
    Version:
    1.0, 30/10/13
